ZH: 飞机在天上飞翔。
EN: The airplane is flying in the sky.

ZH: 昨天我乘坐飞机去北京。
EN: I took an airplane to Beijing yesterday.

ZH: 飞机降落时，我感到很兴奋。
EN: I felt very excited when the airplane landed.

ZH: 飞机票太贵了，我打算坐火车去。
EN: The airplane tickets are too expensive, so I plan to take the train.

ZH: 在飞机上，不允许吸烟。
EN: Smoking is not allowed on the airplane.

ZH: 我的朋友是一名飞机师。
EN: My friend is an airplane pilot.

ZH: 这架飞机的速度非常快。
EN: This airplane is very fast.

ZH: 我在飞机上看了一部电影。
EN: I watched a movie on the airplane.

ZH: 飞机上的气流让我感到有些不舒服。
EN: The air current on the airplane made me feel a little uncomfortable.

ZH: 我站在飞机场看飞机起飞。
EN: I stood at the airport and watched the airplane take off.

ZH: 飞机在云层中穿行。
EN: The airplane is cruising through the clouds.

ZH: 飞机对环境造成了很大的污染。
EN: Airplanes cause a lot of pollution to the environment.

ZH: 飞机上的乘客需要系好安全带。
EN: Passengers on the airplane need to fasten their seat belts.

ZH: 飞机在高空飞行时，氧气供应变得稀薄。
EN: Oxygen supply becomes thinner when the airplane is flying at high altitudes.

ZH: 飞机上提供了免费的食物和饮料。
EN: Free food and drinks are provided on the airplane.

ZH: 我每年坐飞机去旅行。
EN: I travel by airplane every year.

ZH: 飞机的机翼是用铝制成的。
EN: The airplane's wings are made of aluminum.

ZH: 飞机上的座位非常舒服。
EN: The seats on the airplane are very comfortable.

ZH: 飞机上的导航仪可以帮助飞行员定位。
EN: Navigation systems on the airplane can help pilots locate their positions.

ZH: 飞机已经在飞行途中了。
EN: The airplane is already in flight.

ZH: 我从飞机窗户看到美丽的景色。
EN: I saw beautiful scenery from the airplane window.
